OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1773712981
OL,3,COne in five witness retail violence or
OL,4,Cabuse ` BRC
OL,6,FMore than a fifth of people (21%)
OL,7,Fwitnessed violence or abuse against
OL,8,Fretail workers in the last year,
OL,9,Faccording to a survey.
OL,11,FIncidents included racial and sexual
OL,12,Fabuse, physical assault and threats
OL,13,Fwith weapons while shopping, the poll
OL,14,Fby Opinium for the British Retail
OL,15,FConsortium (BRC) found.
OL,17,FHowever, the figure was a slight
OL,18,Fimprovement on the previous year, when
OL,19,F23% of customers witnessed such
OL,20,Fincidents.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
