OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1773712981
OL,3,COne in five witness retail violence or
OL,4,Cabuse ` BRC
OL,6,FThe survey also found that nearly a
OL,7,Fquarter of people (23%) have witnessed
OL,8,Fshoplifting ` almost unchanged from
OL,9,F24% the previous year.
OL,11,FRates varied significantly across the
OL,12,FUK, with 32% of Londoners witnessing
OL,13,Fviolence and abuse while shopping,
OL,14,Ffollowed by 26% of those in Yorkshire
OL,15,Fand Humberside and 23% across the
OL,16,FNorth East.
OL,18,FThe East of England recorded the
OL,19,Flowest rate at 13%.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1773712981
OL,3,COne in five witness retail violence or
OL,4,Cabuse ` BRC
OL,6,FThe picture was a little different for
OL,7,Fthose witnessing shop theft, topped by
OL,8,FLondon and the West Midlands (29%),
OL,9,Ffollowed by Yorkshire and Humberside
OL,10,Fand the North West (26%), the South
OL,11,FEast (25%) and the South West (24%).
OL,13,FRetailers reported that organised
OL,14,Fcriminal gangs were increasingly
OL,15,Ftargeting high-value goods that they
OL,16,Fcan easily resell.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/8
