CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1773712981
OL,3,COne in five witness retail violence or
OL,4,Cabuse ` BRC
OL,6,FPrevious BRC data revealed there were
OL,7,F1,600 incidents of violence and abuse
OL,8,Fagainst retail workers every day last
OL,9,Fyear ` the second highest level on
OL,10,Frecord.
OL,12,FThis included 118 incidents involving
OL,13,Fphysical violence and 36 involving a
OL,14,Fweapon every day.
OL,16,FThe BRC said delivery drivers were
OL,17,Falso often subjected to abuse,
OL,18,Fphysical violence and threats with
OL,19,Fweapons.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
