CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1773712981
OL,3,COne in five witness retail violence or
OL,4,Cabuse ` BRC
OL,6,FIt said retailers had spent an
OL,7,Festimated #5 billion on fighting
OL,8,Fretail crime over the past five years,
OL,9,Fincluding on CCTV, security personnel,
OL,10,Fanti-theft devices and body-worn
OL,11,Fcameras.
OL,13,FThese costs added to existing
OL,14,Ffinancial pressures, limited
OL,15,Finvestment and contributed to higher
OL,16,Fprices for customers, it warned.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
