PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1773712981
OL,3,COne in five witness retail violence or
OL,4,Cabuse ` BRC
OL,6,FThe upcoming Crime and Policing Bill
OL,7,Fwill remove the #200 threshold of "low
OL,8,Flevel" theft, "sending a clear signal
OL,9,Fthat all shoplifting will be treated
OL,10,Fseriously", the BRC said.
OL,12,FHowever, it said the Bill needed to go
OL,13,Ffurther by extending protection to all
OL,14,Fcustomer-facing retail workers,
OL,15,Fincluding delivery drivers.
OL,26,@oD@cOUpD@FO]pD@OOUrD@JO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/8
