OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30407
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1773712981
OL,3,COne in five witness retail violence or
OL,4,Cabuse ` BRC
OL,6,FBRC chief executive Helen Dickinson
OL,7,Fsaid: "For too many people, violence
OL,8,Fand abuse are now part of the shopping
OL,9,Fexperience. An incident might last
OL,10,Fseconds, but for workers and
OL,11,Fbystanders, the impact can last a
OL,12,Flifetime.
OL,14,F"The Crime and Policing Bill is an
OL,15,Fimportant step towards protecting
OL,16,Fretail workers and tackling crime. But
OL,17,Fas drafted, it falls short. Retail
OL,18,Fworkers in England and Wales deserve
OL,19,Fthe same protections as those in
OL,20,FScotland, including delivery drivers.
OL,26,@oD@GOUvD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/8
